query:
WITH combined_prices AS (
                    SELECT time, last_price as price
                    FROM price_ticks
                    WHERE time > $1
                    UNION ALL
                    SELECT time, value as price
                    FROM price_history
                    WHERE time > $1
                )
                SELECT
                    MAX(time) as latest_time,
                    MIN(price) as min_price,
                    MAX(price) as max_price
                FROM combined_prices
